reviews.text: lunch sets was good!tried their beef cubes and the taste was great,it comes with vegestable and soup. you can ask for additional sauce if you want,i like the sauce. Friendly staff and accomodating. Small resto and the place looks clean and cosy. a lot of choices and the price was affordable. will surely come back next time to try their sashimi
Tasty lunch set at a great price. I don't know how their sashimi and sushi, but like other reviewers here their cooked food is nice, espeically for their lunch sets
It doesn't worth the price, food quality is below average. Sashimi is really not a fresh one, cooked food is acceptable. Anyway, you can find many way better food in Kowloon City area.
